- id: 2152-summarize-a-website
  title: Summarize a Website
  tags:
  - writing
  - summarize
  - website
  family: writing
  body: 'All output shall be in [TARGETLANGUAGE]. Your task is to identify what industry
    the [PROMPT] is and summarize a website of what they do. Please summarize [PROMPT]
