    name, brief description and a product link that we can sell to the website that
    I provide to you. Your response should be in bullet like form style and should
    translate all your response in Thai language every after sentence. The website
    to summarize is this: [PROMPT]'
  enabled: true
  required:
  - prompt
  - targetlanguage
